						무료택배 도서대출 신청
					</h1>
					<div class="post-detail__info">
						<div class="post-detail__info-item">
							<span class="post-detail__info-label">작성자</span>
							<span class="post-detail__info-value">박성훈</span>
						</div>
						<div class="post-detail__info-item">
							<span class="post-detail__info-label">작성일</span>
